​Quan trong la doi voi minh, Apple Watch thuc su khong de thay the smartphone. Minh co quan diem la smart watch la mot phan mo rong de giup minh truy cap thong tin nhanh hon, tien hon. No giong nhu cach mobile browser giup chung ta khong con phai cam mat vao PC/laptop de xem web vay, gio minh co the xem duoc thoi tiet ngay khi ngu day, chi can dua co tay ra la len duoc may bay (rat tienkhi dang tui tam linh kinh). Ca nhan minh tin tuong vao tuong lai cua smart watch noi chung chu khong chi Apple Watch boi vi cac hang khac cung se nhanh chong dua nhung tien dung cua smart watch den nguoi dung va ngay ca AW cung can nhieu cai tien hon nua (hien AW con can rat nhieu cai tien). Neu cac ban dinh vi smartwatch dung voi nhung gi no co the cung cap, cac ban se co the khai thac duoc nhieu hon tu no de cuoc song tien loi hon, nhieu thoi gian cho nhung moi quan tam va thu vui khac hon Truoc het, de tranh cac tranh luan khong tot, minh xin duoc noi luon may y: - Bai nay minh viet ve kinh nghiem va trai nghiem ca nhan cua minh sau mot thoi gian dung Apple Watch. No co the phu hop voi ban, co the khong -> xin dung binh luan kieu "Toi khong can cai do" - Minh song o My, chac chan cuoc song khac da so cac ban -> xin dung noi "Cha co tac dung o VN" - Bai nay chi noi ve cach minh ung dung Apple Watch vao cuoc song cua minh -> xin dung noi va tranh luan ve thiet ke hay gia ca dat re - Bai nay chi noi ve cach tot nhat de tan dung Apple Watch -> xin dung so danh voi cac dong ho khac, ke ca co dien lan smart watch Ok, minh xin duoc bat dau voi hinh anh dau tien, Apple Watch tren tay minh. Cai minh mua la Apple Watch ban Stainless steel, day Milanese. Minh dung mat dong ho rat nhieu thong tin vi minh de cao productivity hon la co de no nhin giong dong ho thuong Apple Watch co phan Glance, la cac thong tin co the duoc truy cap nhanh bang cach vuot tu duoi len tren. Ngoai cac thong tin san co cua Apple Watch nhu heart beat, activities, minh co dua 1 so thong tin minh hay can xem ra Glance: - Thoi tiet la thu hang sang minh luon phai xem - iHearRadio vi minh nghe thuong xuyen - Flight track, minh bay gan nhu hang tuan nen rat can cai nay Mot trong cac ly do minh dung iPhone la vi co Passbook. Apple Watch da giup viec dung Passbook tro nen thuan tien hon truoc rat nhieu - Di xem phim cuoi tuan chi can scan barcode trong AW vao may soat ve la xong - Di uong Starbucks, chi can scan AW la cung thanh toan nhanh chong - Boarding chuyen bay vo cung de dang vi boarding pass san ngay trong AW, scan vao dau doc o gate la xong - Di an McDonald ma vua quen vi vua khong co tien mat, da co Apple Pay Minh cung thuong xuyen dung cac app sau tren AW: - Uber la thu khong the thieu voi minh, gio goi xe qua don gian - Theo doi chi tieu voi Mint - Tra cuu password cac kieu tien loi voi 1Password - Xem cac do minh mua bao gio duoc delivered voi Deliveries - Tim cho an uong voi Yelp, cai nay hay di cong tac nhu minh rat la can - Doc bao voi Flipboard - Xem thong tin the tin dung - Xem cac cong viec can lam (to do list) - Trinh chieu Powerpoint cung voi iPhone va AW (rat an tuong voi khach hang ) Con mot so ung dung kha hay nua nhung minh chua su dung thuong xuyen nen khong gioi thieu o day (track golf score chang han) Quan trong la doi voi minh, Apple Watch thuc su khong de thay the smartphone. Minh co quan diem la smart watch la mot phan mo rong de giup minh truy cap thong tin nhanh hon, tien hon. No giong nhu cach mobile browser giup chung ta khong con phai cam mat vao PC/laptop de xem web vay, gio minh co the xem duoc thoi tiet ngay khi ngu day, chi can dua co tay ra la len duoc may bay (rat tienkhi dang tui tam linh kinh). Ca nhan minh tin tuong vao tuong lai cua smart watch noi chung chu khong chi Apple Watch boi vi cac hang khac cung se nhanh chong dua nhung tien dung cua smart watch den nguoi dung va ngay ca AW cung can nhieu cai tien hon nua (hien AW con can rat nhieu cai tien). Neu cac ban dinh vi smartwatch dung voi nhung gi no co the cung cap, cac ban se co the khai thac duoc nhieu hon tu no de cuoc song tien loi hon, nhieu thoi gian cho nhung moi quan tam va thu vui khac hon

Van de lon nhat la khong chi o Viet Nam ma khap noi tren TG bay gio khong co AW de mua, voi em rieng cai app phuc vu ren luyen the thao la vo cung dang tien roi. Chu thot viet bai cau va nghia ro rang qua, dung la song o My du la nguoi co nguon goc o dau cung de dang cho nen van minh hon, tks chu thot vi bai danh gia.

Nhung thu khac minh khong noi (kho de giai thich cho nhung nguoi van ra san bay check in tai quay lay boarding pass cai Passbook no tien the nao duoc) nhung ve viec trinh chieu PPT thi minh giai thich them: Voi cong viec cua minh (cua minh thoi nhe, khong nhat thiet giong cac ban), minh phai dung PPT rat nhieu va nhieu khi khong duoc chuan bi truoc. Do vay phone cua minh thuong xuyen duoc dung de trinh chieu (lightning to VGA hoac to HDMI) Neu ban da tung dua PPT tu phone ra may chieu ban se thay ngay 1 su bat tien la minh luon phai o gan may chieu vi adapter video out rat ngan. Voi AW thi minh co the de phone cam vao may chieu va ngoi dau trong phong cung trinh chieu duoc. Day la thuc te cong viec cua minh, khong phai bia ra cho vui.

Neu dung Apple Watch thi con khoi can Touch ID nua co. Tho tay vao may la xong. Apple Watch se bat nhap code khi minh deo, sau do no se hieu la minh van dang deo va khong hoi code nua. Neu minh thao ra va deo lai thi no se biet va bat nhap code lai. Cai nay kha la tien ma van an toan.
